p-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什和萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_billieeilish_sabrinacarpenter_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_billieeilish_sabrinacarpenter_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_billieeilish_sabrinacarpenter_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_billieeilish_sabrinacarpenter_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_billieeilish_sabrinacarpenter_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_billieeilish_sabrinacarpenter_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的单曲《Birds Of Feather》是<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a> 2024 年流媒体播放量最高的歌曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard And Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、更明亮</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲取自她的第三张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Hit Me Hard and Soft</a> 》，点击量达到 1,775,172,881 次，击败了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>的热门歌曲《Espresso》。</p><p>后者在流媒体平台上的收听量为 1,774,525,704 次，落后 650,000 次。</p><p> Eilish 的单曲在英国官方单曲榜上排名第二，在美国公告牌百强单曲榜上也排名第二。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：物以类聚" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/6dOtVTDdiauQNBQEDOtlAB?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：浓缩咖啡" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/2qSkIjg1o9h3YT9RAgYN75?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>它最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024">被<i>NME</i>评为 2024 年最佳歌曲第 12 名</a>。她的专辑《Hit Me Hard And Soft》也入围<em>NME</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">2024 年最佳专辑排行榜，排名第九</a>。</p><p>该热门歌曲还获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">三项格莱美奖提名，包括年度歌曲、年度唱片和最佳流行独奏表演</a>。</p><p>与此同时，卡彭特的单曲在英国单曲榜上名列前茅，并获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">格莱美奖年度唱片和最佳流行独奏表演</a>提名，而《Bed Chem》被评为<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024"><i>NME</i> 2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲</a>之一。</p><p>在谈到她的热门作品时，卡彭特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-felt-she-had-literally-no-idea-if-the-public-would-like-espresso-3825392">最近表示，影片上映后，她觉得她“根本不知道”公众是否会喜欢它</a>。</p><p> “我记得决定在夏初推出这首歌，并认为浓缩咖啡更像是一种秋季饮料，”她说。 “我真的不知道它是否会产生联系，但这首歌的情感和声音以及它所带来的信心是我真正相信的。”</p><p>她继续说道：“所以我真的不知道有人会喜欢它，但我喜欢它，这就是那一刻对我来说最重要的事情，也是我一遍又一遍地记住的事情。” </p><p><iframe title="比莉·艾利什 |第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mVvt33l7BwM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时，Eilish 刚刚<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-cover-o-holy-night-at-los-angeles-show-3824457">在英格尔伍德的起亚论坛上进行了五场演出</a>，结束了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-debut-hit-me-hard-and-soft-tracks-and-rock-through-happier-than-ever-as-she-kicks-off-world-tour-in-quebec-setlist-3798632">“Hit Me Hard And Soft”巡演</a>的美国站。</p><p>在一场家乡演出中，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-bring-out-charli-xcx-to-perform-guess-remix-in-la-3823303">邀请了 Charli XCX 作为特邀嘉宾来表演他们的“Guess”混音版</a>。该曲目获得 2025 年格莱美奖<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">最佳流行二重唱/团体表演提名。</a>两位艺术家还角逐年度专辑、年度唱片、最佳流行独奏表演等奖项。</p><p>艾利什最近还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-plays-snippet-of-fun-new-songs-weve-been-making-music-3821114">一次采访中播放了两首新歌的片段，并透露她又开始“创作音乐”了</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-warns-of-extreme-dieting-its-not-a-fun-way-to-live-3825595">警告粉丝极端节食的危险</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilishs-birds-of-a-feather-beats-sabrina-carpenters-espresso-to-most-streamed-spotify-song-of-2024-3825766">Billie Eilish 的《Birds Of A Feather》击败 Sabrina Carpenter 的《Espresso》成为 2024 年 Spotify 流媒体播放量最多的歌曲，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
