汤姆·赫兰德曾在一场超市争吵中被认出来后才平息https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-holland-fight-spider-man-3825717?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tom-holland-fight-spider-manVictoria Luxford Thu, 02 Jan 2025 21:21:47 +0000 Film NewsNewsMarvel Cinematic UniverseSpider-ManThe Avengers https://www.nme.com/?p=3825717 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>当这位蜘蛛侠明星介入洛杉矶一家超市的一场斗殴事件时，他的银幕形象派上了用场。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-holland-fight-spider-man-3825717">汤姆·赫兰德（Tom Holland）曾在被认出后驱散超市斗殴的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tom-Holland-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/marvel">漫威</a>演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-holland">汤姆·赫兰德</a>最著名的角色派上了用场，当时他那张辨识度很高的面孔帮助平息了洛杉矶一家超市的一场斗殴。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-downey-jr-stopped-tom-hollands-lines-getting-cut-in-first-spider-man-scene-youre-going-to-want-to-spend-time-on-this-3805285"><strong>小罗伯特·唐尼在《蜘蛛侠》第一个场景中阻止了汤姆·赫兰德的台词被剪掉：“你会想在这上面花时间的”</strong></a></li></ul><p>这位<em>《蜘蛛侠》</em>电影的明星在回忆<a href="https://www.menshealth.com/health/a63115634/tom-holland-interview-bero/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《男性健康》</em></a>事件时表示，他在公开场合露面时要谨慎选择，以免引起过多关注。不过，他确实提到，他的名气在一次前往洛杉矶全食超市的一家分店时派上了用场，当时霍兰德附近的两名男子之间爆发了一场斗殴。</p><p> “他们就像在我身后攻击一样，”他说，并解释说他抓住了其中一个试图平息局势。 “我可以看到他立即认出了我，你可以看到车轮在转动，就像，我真的很生气，但蜘蛛侠告诉我要冷静。” </p><figure id="attachment_3189152" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3189152" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3189152" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1.jpg" alt="蜘蛛侠" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/spider-man-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3189152" class="wp-caption-text"> （来源：索尼）</figcaption></figure><p>霍兰德自 2016 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-movie-16448-306476"><em>《美国队长：内战》</em></a>以来一直扮演这位超级英雄，也被称为彼得·帕克，并在轰动一时的<em>《复仇者</em>联盟》电影中扮演关键角色，最后一次出现是在 2021 年的<em>《蜘蛛侠：无路回家》</em>中，与蜘蛛侠演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andrew-garfield">安德鲁·加菲尔德和安德鲁·加菲尔德</a>演对手戏。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tobey-maguire">托比·马奎尔</a>。</p><p>在采访的其他地方，他表示，如果他成为一名父亲，他将“从地球表面消失”。他声称：“当我有了孩子后，你就不会再在电影中看到我了。”</p><p>在此之前，这位 28 岁的年轻人已经有了很多计划，最近他参演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰 (Christopher Nolan)</a>即将上映的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-nolans-next-film-will-be-an-adaptation-of-homers-the-odyssey-3824603"><em>《奥德赛》(The Odyssey</em></a> )。他还计划在尚未命名的第四部<em>蜘蛛侠</em>电影中进一步饰演彼得·帕克，并在 2026 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-downey-jr-set-to-return-to-marvel-as-dr-doom-3778571"><em>《复仇者联盟：世界末日》</em></a>中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-downey-jr">小罗伯特·唐尼</a>重聚。</p><p>最近，他也对搭档赞<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">达亚</a>赞不绝口，称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-holland-says-acting-opposite-zendaya-has-been-his-saving-grace-3823641">在<em>蜘蛛侠</em>电影中与她演对手戏是他的“救命稻草”</a></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-holland-fight-spider-man-3825717">汤姆·赫兰德（Tom Holland）曾在被认出后驱散超市斗殴的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
